OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAn overcast morning with
OL,6,Fperiods of rain that turn heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes, combining with gales to bring
OL,8,Fdecidedly un-Spring like weather.
OL,9,FClearing to blustery showers during
OL,10,Fthe afternoon, these occasional in
OL,11,Fwest, isolated in east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBlustery showers pushing
OL,14,Facross the area on strong west to
OL,15,Fsouthwest winds. Outbreaks frequent
OL,16,Fand heavy in west, occasional in east
OL,17,Fand turning wintry to quite low levels.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
