OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FShowers continuing, frequent
OL,6,Fin the west, occasional in east, but
OL,7,Foutbreaks lighter than Thursday night.
OL,8,FBest of the brighter spells expected
OL,9,Facross Lothian and Borders.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,12,Ffor Saturday focused in west, with
OL,13,Feast relatively sheltered. Rain early
OL,14,FSunday, clearing to blustery showers
OL,15,Fby afternoon, wintry across hills.
OL,16,FScattered showers then periods of rain
OL,17,Ffor Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
